{
  "stem": "3474.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, in the-- after that, they took us out to work for, like, breaking up stones for the highways, things like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Things-- you know, just-- just to keep us busy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They made us get up every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They beat-- they beat you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They chased you out with the sticks to get up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you would-- you know, you get so numb.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they hit you, you don't even feel it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They don't even feel it, they hit you like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you get-- you get numb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never cried in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just like-- I never-- I never shed a tear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was so-- you get so numb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You don't even know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You just know one thing you have to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's just-- matter of fact, in Buchenwald, when I see what they do with American prisoners, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because I remember there was American prisoner with-- with his-- they had, the, you know, this-- the-- the army clothes on yet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] there was this American one, was a black guy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They beat the hell out him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They said, go, you black so-and-so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in German you say, schwarz hund, schwarz hund.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Go, you know, black-- they used to call him black-- black dog.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Go, go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They used to hit him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was pulling-- pushing a wheelbarrow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the-- and the white guy also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were talking, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they won't talk to each other, but the Germans were yelling at them, [GERMAN], you American, swine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why I know they were Americans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was black, because in Europe there was no black people, so that's why I knew he was American.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
